metadata.name: Rust And Dust
metadata.description:
"At that last moment of my life, I finally be able to cry although I do not understand why I cry. 
Maybe because I remember all memories I had vividly. 
In the end everything will rust and turn into dust and we bring our memories with it." 

- Android 21 signing off

5000x6560

This artwork will not be replicated in any shape or form in the future by the artist as this will be last edition. 
Thank you.
